%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c2099%2c20211116%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,110,上訴,2099,20211116,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"2099","JDATE":"20211116","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例等"}